llimated beam. High-energy focused\nbeams were able to produce TSDRs > 100 and $\\sigma_T$ around 1.5~mm. From this\nstudy, it appears very attractive to implement magnetically focused proton\nbeams in radiotherapy of small lesions or tumors in close vicinity to healthy\norgans at risk. This can also lead to a paradigm change in spatially\nfractionated radiotherapy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Sep 2022 10:31:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-05"}
