 coherent with the expressed emotion. Our work\nexplores the importance of body posture and frequency of idle motion in the\nconception of robotic systems. Such additions could provide social robots that\nafford emotional contagion in effortless robot-human collaborative tasks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Sep 2022 12:22:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
