. Further, we design a set of defense mechanisms against the GPIA\nattacks, and demonstrate that these mechanisms can reduce attack accuracy\neffectively with small loss on GNN model accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 2 Sep 2022 14:59:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-06"}
